description:
This ti was requested by @admiral_underpants

Victoria Coren Mitchell is a highly regarded British television presenter, writer, and professional poker player. Known for her sharp intellect and engaging personality, Coren Mitchell has achieved success in multiple fields. She has hosted popular television shows, written acclaimed columns and books, and made a significant impact in the world of professional poker, becoming the first two-time winner of the European Poker Tour Main Event. Her achievements and contributions have solidified her reputation as a versatile and accomplished figure in the entertainment industry.

Feel free to leave me a tip/buy me a coffee if you like what I am doing :)
